---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
---
<section class="hero">
  <h1>Personal finance, made clear — not another guru's noise.</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">MoneyClarity is for people who want honest, practical money guidance — including a dedicated track for halal personal finance — without the hype, the affiliate spam, or the "get rich" theatrics.</p>
  <a class="btn" href="/halal-personal-finance/">Start with Halal Personal Finance →</a>
</section>

<section class="latest">
  <h2>Latest posts</h2>
  <ul class="post-list">
    {% for post in collections.posts %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}">
        <span class="post-list-title">{{ post.data.title }}</span>
        <span class="post-list-date">{{ post.data.date | readableDate }}</span>
      </a>
      {% if post.data.description %}<p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>

<section id="subscribe" class="subscribe">
  <h2>Get MoneyClarity in your inbox</h2>
  <p>One email, only when there's something worth reading. No noise.</p>
  <form name="subscribe" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field">
    <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="subscribe" />
    <p class="hidden"><label>Don't fill this out: <input name="bot-field" /></label></p>
    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required>
    <button class="btn" type="submit">Subscribe</button>
  </form>
</section>
